After 2 years of watching Tali’s work, saving, driving over an hour to her beautiful new studio, & following her exact pre & post session instructions— I couldn’t be happier with my results of micro blading. 

I was so nervous cause I already have full brows but from waxing in middle school my ends (aka tails) would grow back patchy. 

1000% recommend @eyedolizedbrows for your PMU services. & when you do go, let her know I referred you! & tag me to see your results 🖤
